        #privacy-policy-text
            h1.title Fitness Buddy's Privacy Policy
            h3 Topics
            ul
                li What data do we collect?
                li How do we collect your data?
                li How will we use your data?
                li How do we store your data?
                li Marketing
                li What are your data protection rights?
